channel.title: Snow!?
channel.description:
Hey guys, I used to play a server, and in the server it was snowing... I asked how to do this once before, and someone told me 'interfaces'. Seriously, that is all they told me. That may make plenty of sense to you but I am bad with certain stuff in coding.
So, if anyone would mind explaining a little better, I would really appreciate their help :P
Thanks ~ Dai
